### 1. 查看目前的 About Blocks (記錄 Component IDs)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/about?populate=blocks
Authorization: Bearer {{apiToken}}

### 2. 測試：保留 ID 的更新 (推薦做法)
# 保留現有 Component 的 id，只修改內容
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/about
Authorization: Bearer {{apiToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "data": {
    "blocks": [
      {
        "__component": "shared.quote",
        "id": 1,
        "title": "保留ID的更新標題",
        "body": "保留ID的更新內容"
      }
    ]
  }
}

### 3. 查看更新結果 (ID 應該保持為 1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/about?populate=blocks
Authorization: Bearer {{apiToken}}

### 4. 測試：不提供 ID 的更新 (會建立新 Component)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/about
Authorization: Bearer {{apiToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "data": {
    "blocks": [
      {
        "__component": "shared.quote",
        "title": "沒有ID的新Component",
        "body": "這會建立新的Component實例"
      }
    ]
  }
}

### 5. 查看結果 (ID 會變成新的數字，例如 2)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/about?populate=blocks
Authorization: Bearer {{apiToken}}

### 6. 測試：只更新非 Dynamic Zone 欄位
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/about
Authorization: Bearer {{apiToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "data": {
    "title": "只更新標題，不碰 blocks"
  }
}

### 7. 驗證：blocks 應該保持不變
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/about?populate=blocks
Authorization: Bearer {{apiToken}}

### 8. 測試：混合更新 - 既更新 title 又更新 blocks
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/about
Authorization: Bearer {{apiToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "data": {
    "title": "更新的標題",
    "blocks": [
      {
        "__component": "shared.quote",
        "id": 1,
        "title": "保持原有ID的引言",
        "body": "這個Component保持原有的ID"
      },
      {
        "__component": "shared.rich-text",
        "content": "新增的富文字內容，會有新ID"
      }
    ]
  }
}

### 9. 最終驗證
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/about?populate=blocks
Authorization: Bearer {{apiToken}}